entry.title: Q: Why do you support the #VoiceToParliament? "The simple answer is because the Indigenous community has asked us to." "The hard question is why would you say no?" "How at this point in history would you think, ‘Nah they've had it too good for too long'
entry.content: Q: Why do you support the #VoiceToParliament? "The simple answer is because the Indigenous community has asked us to." "The hard question is why would you say no?" "How at this point in history would you think, ‘Nah they've had it too good for too long'?" Richard Denniss at Politics in the Pub.

entry.title: If the Australian government started taxing oil and gas companies properly, like in Norway, they could give Australians free university education. It's not that we can't afford it. It's that our governments haven't chosen to do it. #auspol
